    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>「该死的，可我从来都没有做过衣服!」</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每天只知道买奢侈品，生活十分奢靡的蜘蛛女巫菲洛西亚。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一夜之间债台高筑的她，为了不吃牢饭，唯一的方法就是，重振老旧的裁缝屋来偿还债务!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在传说中裁缝屋的原主人玛克莉亚，所留下来的蜘蛛恶魔琪拉拉的帮助下，裁缝屋重新开张了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这座被时尚和流行笼罩的「罗亚街」上，未来又有什么样的挑战在等待着菲洛西亚呢?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【采集神秘的材料】</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191570/extras/434e97336997282de43647ee04334e4b.poster.avif?t=1771547424\" width=700 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191570/extras/434e97336997282de43647ee04334e4b.webm?t=1771547424\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >想要制作衣服⋯当然需要材料了!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请前往各地进行探险，采集神秘的材料，制作出魔法服装!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但并不是所有材料都是能轻易得到的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【使用魔法纺车和织布机进行材料加工】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将采集到的材料使用魔法加工成线和布。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请收集各种材料，做出更酷炫的加工品吧!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【用魔法缝纫机制作魔法服装】</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191570/extras/ee08bff439e653864e15cef45bd10f41.poster.avif?t=1771547424\" width=1600 height=900 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191570/extras/ee08bff439e653864e15cef45bd10f41.webm?t=1771547424\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191570/extras/ee08bff439e653864e15cef45bd10f41.mp4?t=1771547424\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >经过加工的材料可以做出漂亮的服装。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >服装制作熟练度越高，访问裁缝屋的客人就越多。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不过当然，一开始可能也只能做出一些歪七扭八、粗糙不堪的礼裙⋯</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【魔法服装制作委托】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >现在是时候开始接受服装制作委托了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为拥有不同背景的客人制作衣服，并以此获得报酬吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >服装品质越高，报酬就越高。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【布置成充满着魅力的裁缝屋】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >罗亚街的客人们对流行的敏感度很高。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在特殊的季节和有活动举行的日子里，请用适合的壁纸和装饰品，好好布置裁缝屋吧。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >裁缝屋越华丽越宽敞，声望也会相应提高。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【各种精彩的小故事】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >菲洛西亚在罗亚街与蜘蛛恶魔琪拉拉一起经营着裁缝屋，但却卷入了意想不到的事件和状况之中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >原本爱慕虚荣的蜘蛛女巫菲洛西亚，在经历了各种事情后，也改变了许多。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >会有哪些精彩有趣的故事在等待着菲洛西亚呢?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191570/extras/c4a64078b18c6e8ac804dece03a65315.avif?t=1771547424\" width=784 height=480 /></span></p>",
